Theory:
- Frequency Counting:
- The process of Tracking how many times a unique element appears in a collection.
- Used to solve string manipulation, anagram detection and data analysis problems efficiently.
- the Optimal way to count frequencies is using Hashmap
- Which Achieves O(n) Time Complexity.

- Hashmaps:
